      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TINEY (4) was once again right in the mix last time out when runner-up over 1800m at this track, beaten 2.75 metres after having raced outside the leader for the entire trip. Will enjoy a nice run from this favourable starting position. Tackles a similar assignment and he can go right on with the job. SPEAKS VOLUMES (7) has had two runs this campaign and is yet to finish in the top three. Added to the sequence last time over 2230m at this track, finishing 160 metres away from the winner when finishing last of nine after breaking in the score up. Finds a nice race and can take return to top-three form. TRANQUIL BILL (6) is better than his first-up run when finishing last of 10 over 2160m at Victor Harbor eight weeks ago. Can place. SUNNY MAJESTY (5) is worth some thought after her last-start fifth over 1800m at this track on February 16.",
